{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/codeeditsourceeditor\/gutterview"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The gutter view displays line numbers that match the text view’s line indexes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This view is used as a scroll view’s ruler view. It sits on top of the text view so text scrolls underneath the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"gutter if line wrapping is disabled.","type":"text"}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/GutterView\/init(font:textColor:textView:delegate:)"]},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/GutterView\/gutterWidth","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/GutterView\/isFlipped"]},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/GutterView\/draw(_:)"],"title":"Instance Methods"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Inherits From","identifiers":["doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(cs)NSView"],"type":"inheritsFrom"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSAccessibilityElement","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSAccessibility","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSAnimatablePropertyContainer","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSAppearanceCustomization","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSDraggingDestination","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSStandardKeyBindingResponding","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSTouchBarProvider","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSUserActivityRestoring","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSUserInterfaceItemIdentification","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSCoding","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSObject","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/s7CVarArgP","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/s28CustomDebugStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/s23CustomStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/SQ","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/SH","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/s8SendableP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Text View","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/CodeEditSourceEditor","doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/TextViewController"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"GutterView"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the gutter needs more space (when the number of digits in the numbers increases eg. adding a line after line 99),"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"it will notify it’s delegate via the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/GutterViewDelegate\/gutterViewWidthDidUpdate(newWidth:)","isActive":true},{"text":" method. In","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CodeEditSourceEditor"},{"type":"text","text":", this notifies the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/TextViewController","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", which in turn updates the textview’s edge insets","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to adjust for the new leading inset."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This view also listens for selection updates, and draws a selected background on selected lines to keep the illusion"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that the gutter’s line numbers are inline with the line itself.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The gutter view has insets of it’s own that are relative to the widest line index. By default, these insets are 20px","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"leading, and 12px trailing. However, this view also has a "},{"code":"GutterView\/backgroundEdgeInsets","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property, that pads"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the rect that has a background drawn. This allows the text to be scrolled under the gutter view for 8px before being","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"overlapped by the gutter. It should help the textview keep the cursor visible if the user types while the cursor is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"off the leading edge of the editor."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@M@CodeEditSourceEditor@objc(cs)GutterView","modules":[{"name":"CodeEditSourceEditor"}],"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GutterView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"GutterView","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"GutterView"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/GutterView","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://CodeEditSourceEditor/objc(pl)NSDraggingDestination":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSDraggingDestination","title":"AppKit.NSDraggingDestination","type":"unresolvable"},"doc://CodeEditSourceEditor/objc(pl)NSUserInterfaceItemIdentification":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/objc(pl)NSUserInterfaceItemIdentification","type":"unresolvable","title":"AppKit.NSUserInterfaceItemIdentification"},"doc://CodeEditSourceEdi